opejskiej solidarno\u015bci'. To wielopi\u0119trowy fa\u0142sz |trans-title = Szumowski criticise the EU: 'There is no European solidarity'. Which is false at many levels<!-- trans-title is the English translation --> | date= 2020-03-26 |newspaper= [[OKO.press]] | url= https://oko.press/szumowski-krytykuje-ue-nie-ma-tej-europejskiej-solidarnosci-to-wielopietrowy-falsz/ |quote= Bo jak by\u015bmy czekali na inne kraje, na Europ\u0119, na \u015bwiat, to by\u015bmy si\u0119 obudzili bez \u015brodk\u00f3w, a dooko\u0142a wszyscy by te \u015brodki sobie zakupili ... \u017beby by\u0142a jasno\u015b\u0107, to nie jest tak, \u017ce my ten sprz\u0119t mamy w Europie, \u017ce s\u0105 jego nieograniczone ilo\u015bci. ... Bo niestety tutaj centralne zakupy zawiod\u0142y, nie ma tej europejskiej solidarno\u015bci.  |accessdate=2020-03-26 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20200326225848/https://oko.press/szumowski-krytykuje-ue-nie-ma-tej-europejskiej-solidarnosci-to-wielopietrowy-falsz/ |archivedate= 2020-03-26 |url-status=live <!-- live|dead|unfit|usurped --> |url-access = <!-- (subscription/registration/limited) default=free -->}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"EUCommission_rescEU\">{{cite web | title= COVID-19: Commission creates first ever rescEU stockpile of medical equipment | website= [[European Commission]] |date =2020-03-19 | url = https://ec.europa.eu/commission/presscorner/detail/pl/ip_20_476 | accessdate = 2020-03-26 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20200322164544/https://ec.europa.eu/commission/presscorner/detail/en/ip_20_476 |archivedate= 2020-03-26 |url-status=live <!-- live|dead|unfit|usurped --> |url-access = <!-- (subscription/registration/limited) default=free -->}}</ref>\n\n<!-- shift to Template:2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic data/Poland medical cases\n<ref name=\"OKOpress_20Mar_24Mar_MZ2deaths\">{{cite news | last1= Zag\u00f3rski | first1= S\u0142awomir | language =pl | title= Lekarka z Warszawy: W\u0142adze nie informuj\u0105 o wszystkich zgonach na 